title: He poured in the Oil and the Wine He poured in the Oil and the Wine The kind that restoreth my soul He saw me bleeding and dying On the Jericho Road When He poured in The Oil and the Wine
lyrics: He poured in the Oil and the Wine He poured in the Oil and the Wine The kind that restoreth my soul He saw me bleeding and dying On the Jericho Road When He poured in The Oil and the Wine
